Error :-  Android license status unknown.

Solution :- 
I shared the above error with ChatGPT. ChatGPT explained that Flutter could not verify whether the Android SDK licenses had been accepted and recommended running:

flutter doctor --android-licenses

I accepted all the Android SDK license agreements and then ran:

flutter doctor

again to verify the fix.

Summary (2–3 lines)

I used ChatGPT to troubleshoot the "Android license status unknown" error that appeared in flutter doctor. 
ChatGPT guided me to run flutter doctor --android-licenses and accept all the Android SDK licenses. 
After following these steps and rerunning flutter doctor, the warning was resolved and my Flutter environment was correctly configured.
